{"tid":2435243,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警隊延後退休計劃下月接受申請 稱難免影響年輕警員晉升及重新分配宿舍","createTime":"2021-03-06T06:03:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T08:46:28.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"02b01e933ddae40d6f5b5ac3c21459f5384d3064","tid":2435243,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T06:03:00.000Z","msg":"警隊早前傳出，率先讓長俸制警務人員選擇延長退休年齡，近日再有更多細節曝光。《蘋果》獲悉，警隊近日向內部發通告，宣佈有關計劃將於4月1日正式推出，申請期為2個月。凡於2000年6月1日前入職的警務人員，只要於今年4月1日前仍然在職或未開始退休前休假，均合資格申請，但只屬一次性安排，並有遴選委員會評核。對於年輕警員擔心，新安排會影響升遷，警方在通告中承認，「難免產生一些附帶問題」，但僅稱會密切監察情況，將影響減低。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210306/MYBX7T36WRH7FL27G2XTRQJARA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210306%2FMYBX7T36WRH7FL27G2XTRQJARA%2F&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1ny1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=309f4305\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210306%2FMYBX7T36WRH7FL27G2XTRQJARA%2F&h=d8b3db20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210306/MYBX7T36WRH7FL27G2XTRQJARA/</a>"},{"pid":"f5ceec7e97921e350f539c02c97e52dd076b1959","tid":2435243,"uid":117509,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T06:05:39.000Z","msg":"比班廢老食多幾年幻幻先到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bc7dcd72481e700606868c29c28f767ee25da40","tid":2435243,"uid":143241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T06:13:41.000Z","msg":"pc成世都冇得升㗎喇,有咩影響？"},{"pid":"14a7f265937fbd68a862fcca467268167cd02ba9","tid":2435243,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T06:15:53.000Z","msg":"有咩理由唔洗轉mpf長糧儲多5年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e0618a0b40c5fbbc28ca2aaedd81ca62d7a2dd","tid":2435243,"uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T06:17:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span cla